---
Source:
  Title: A Year with Hafiz
  Translator: Daniel Ladinsky
  Author: Hafiz
  ISBN: 978-0143117544
  Publisher: Penguin Books
Format: Verse
By: Hafiz
Title: One Regret
Description: February 1
---
One regret, dear world, that I am determined not to have when I am
lying on my deathbed is that I did not kiss you enough.
